
---

## 🔧 How to Use

1. Open the hosted page on your browser or GitHub Pages.  
2. Click **“Start Scanner (Back Camera)”** — grant camera permission.  
3. Hold a QR code in front of the camera to scan.  
4. Or click **“Upload QR Image”** to manually upload and decode.  

